#: ../../../../../../../Users/mariolukas/workspace/beeguard/hivora-sense/docs/source/material.rst:49
msgid ""
"Beim **Seeed Studio XIAO ESP32-S3 Sense** sind alle Teile (Hauptplatine, "
"Kameraplatine, Kühlkörper, WiFi-Antenne) enthalten – mit Ausnahme der SD-"
"Karte."
msgstr ""
"With the **Seeed Studio XIAO ESP32-S3 Sense**, all parts (main board, "
"camera board, heat sink, Wi-Fi antenna) are included – with the exception "
"of the SD card."

